last_episode_to_air.name: FINALE EPISODE | Choosing Her Boooyfriend
last_episode_to_air.overview: After a contentious dinner at a romantic restaurant nearly brings B to dismiss them both, B Simone’s moment of truth arrives: it’s time to choose her boooyfriend. It’s the decision of a lifetime. Will it be Thug Love, or Invisalign?

name: You're My Boooyfriend
overview: After seven years of searching, social media star B Simone is still looking for a boyfriend, bringing an eclectic cast of dating competition hopefuls to her hot Atlanta mansion.  Witness as nearly a dozen wannabes attempt courtship against zany trials and tense eliminations, all in the hopes of joining B at her side. Can B Simone finally find her boooyfriend?

seasons.name: Season 1
seasons.overview:
After seven years of searching, social media star B Simone is still looking for a boyfriend, bringing an eclectic cast of dating competition hopefuls to her hot Atlanta mansion.

Witness as nearly a dozen wannabes attempt courtship against zany trials and tense eliminations, all in the hopes of joining B at her side. Can B Simone finally find her boooyfriend?

episodes.name: 1. Are You B’s Boooyfriend? Part 1
episodes.overview: The suitors move into the mansion to meet B Simone and her bestie Pretty Vee, but it isn’t long before tensions rise and the competitors clash over more than just her attention.

episodes.name: 2.  Are You B’s Boooyfriend? Part 2
episodes.overview: The fallout from the fight in her own home continues as one contestant even suffers PTSD symptoms. An emotional B Simone is at her wits end: Someone needs to go home.

episodes.name: 3. More Than Gloves Come Off
episodes.overview: After the previous evening’s testosterone-filled drama, B Simone wants to stop the guys from fighting and just have some fun. Pretty Vee has the perfect antedode: The strip club! But the girls have a surprise in store for the guys, and not everyone will be pleased.

episodes.name: 4. Things Are Heating Up
episodes.overview: With Pretty Vee gone, B Simone is suddenly on her own. Before inviting her friend K-Camp over to help her, B Simone spends the day getting to know the guys one-on-one. From a romantic balcony interlude to an emotional comfort session outside, B finds more than she bargained for. Meanwhile, Juwanna Man has plans of her own as a spy on the hunt for B Simone’s approval.

episodes.name: 5. Setting The B. Simone Tone
episodes.overview: After losing Pretty Vee, B Simone turns to ATL trap song legend KCamp to drop by the mansion and help her choose who has the best rap skills from among her potential boooyfriends.

episodes.name: 6. Having the Balls to Fight
episodes.overview:
B Simone invites her friend Summerella to the mansion to help her decide on a physical challenge for the guys.

But another fight in the house leads to putting their plan into action even sooner than expected.

episodes.name: 7. A Truthfully Daring Way To Go
episodes.overview:
B Simone invites her besties The Ferow, Ms Jacky Oh, Watch Jazzy and Its Litty Lex to a game of truth or dare with the boys, in an effort to weed out the weakest link.

But when her girls take the game too far, a flustered B must reach out to Toya Turnup to help her make a surprising choice of who she’s sending home.

episodes.name: 8. B Way Calling
episodes.overview: Just when the fighting in the house has stopped and the boys are finally getting along, B Simone decides to investigate their pasts by demanding each of their phones.

episodes.name: 9. A Recipe for Disaster
episodes.overview: B Simone leaves word she expects the boys to cook her a vegan meal to prove their love. Despite providing them all the ingredients to make it easier, some can stand the heat, but come elimination, one guy will be out of her kitchen.
